@startuml connectivity_and_ivi_health_to_tmu_service_mode_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Connectivity And IVI Health To TMU Service Mode Signal Flow\n(connectivity state + IVI health + vehicle state -> TMU link and service-mode publication)

participant "Connectivity bus" as Conn #F4F7FB
participant "IVI health bus" as Ivi #E8F0FE
participant "Vehicle state bus" as Veh #FCE8FF
participant "TMU\ntelematics owner" as TMU #E8F7E8
participant "TMU service bus" as TmuBus #FFF4CC
participant "Observers /\nconnectivity readers" as Obs #FFF4CC

== TMU Inputs ==

Conn -> TMU : frmConnectivityStateMsg\nConnectivityType / ConnectivityState / SignalBars
Ivi -> TMU : frmIviHealthDetailMsg\nIviCpuLoad / IviMemLoad
Veh -> TMU : frmVehicleStateCanMsg\ngDriveState
activate TMU
TMU -> TMU : freshness checks for\nconnectivity, IVI health, vehicle state
TMU -> TMU : linkState = 0/1/2\nfrom connectivity state and signal bars
TMU -> TMU : serviceMode degraded when\nIVI CPU/MEM load high or weak connectivity
TMU -> TMU : remoteClimateReq only when\nserviceMode == 1, connType == 1,\nsignalBars >= 3, IVI load low, driveState == 0
note right of TMU
Representative gating inputs
- ConnectivityType / ConnectivityState
- SignalBars
- IviCpuLoad / IviMemLoad
- gDriveState
end note

== TMU Publish ==

TMU -> TmuBus : frmTmuServiceStateMsg\nTmuLinkState / TmuServiceMode /\nRemoteClimateReq / SignalBars
note right of TMU
Representative outputs
- TmuLinkState
- TmuServiceMode
- RemoteClimateReq
- SignalBars
end note

== Downstream Visibility ==

TmuBus -> Obs : telematics service visibility /\nremote-service consumers
deactivate TMU

note over Conn, Obs
Representative runtime chain
1. Connectivity, IVI health, and vehicle state reach TMU
2. TMU evaluates link quality and service degradations
3. TMU derives final service mode and remote-climate eligibility
4. TMU publishes telematics service state for downstream consumers
end note

@enduml
